{"tid":2412660,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"食環署：惠顧外賣顧客或速遞員不掃瞄安心出行也可接受","createTime":"2021-02-18T07:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T08:07:37.000Z","uid":301479,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6a9e23f9d65281eb740f2dd4973e609f39a52cd1","tid":2412660,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:04:58.000Z","msg":"政府今日起放寬社交距離措施，食肆堂食延長至晚上10時，容許4人一枱，但負責人必須要求顧客用「安心出行」應用程式掃碼或留低聯絡資料。<br />\n<br />\n食環署回應傳媒查詢時表示，純粹外賣不涉及脫下口罩，顧客逗留時間也較堂食為短，因此只惠顧外賣的顧客或提取外賣的速遞員，不掃瞄食肆的「安心出行」場所二維碼，也是可以接受。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576207-20210218.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576207-20210218.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=90581aa0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576207-20210218.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4d075c69\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576207-20210218.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a8613bdac7f260bb40de397928867771bb1ea8a6","tid":2412660,"uid":21638,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:08:36.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母佢地傾掂數未架<br />\n咪撚成日改啦"},{"pid":"122d2b608b62b83ba5e1c624df180e90ee47d7df","tid":2412660,"uid":301479,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a8613bdac7f260bb40de397928867771bb1ea8a6","tid":2412660,"uid":21638,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:08:36.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母佢地傾掂數未架<br />\n咪撚成日改啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:10:08.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">This is 香港特衰政府!</span></span></p>"},{"pid":"bbb74564a987e235cb05365da193414a83d23827","tid":2412660,"uid":37869,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:11:02.000Z","msg":"轉個頭：可接受唔等於可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/n